<% end %>

<% unless @view_object.declined_cannot_reapply? %>
# What you can do next
You can explore [other routes into teaching](https://getintoteaching.education.gov.uk/routes-into-teaching).

<% unless @view_object.from_ineligible_country? %>
Or, if you can address the reasons your application has been declined, you can submit a new application. You must [check you’re still eligible to apply](<%= new_teacher_interface_application_form_url %>) first. You’ll need to provide all the required information and documents again.
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% unless @view_object.from_ineligible_country? %>
