# If you disagree with our decision

If you think our decision to decline your application for QTS in England is wrong, you can request to challenge the decision. This is known as a decision review.

To challenge this decision, you must provide:

- evidence and reasoning for how you meet the required assessment criteria
- any additional information not included in your original application that would support the decision review

You must make the request within 28 days of the date we sent the decision email. Your request will be reviewed by a senior Professional Recognition Manager.

[Sign in to request a decision review](<%= teacher_interface_application_form_decision_review_requests_url %>).
<% end %>

